# Project Rules

## Request Interception & Auth Guards

The `middleware.ts` pattern is deprecated in this project. All request-level
interceptions, auth guards, and redirects must be implemented in
`apps/web/src/proxy.ts`.

- Do NOT create or modify `apps/web/src/middleware.ts`
- Add new route guards or redirect logic to the `proxy` function in `proxy.ts`
- Update the `config.matcher` array in `proxy.ts` when adding new protected routes
